Interface ModelGeneratorSymbolic

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelGenerator, ModelInfo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModulesFileModelGeneratorSymbolic

    public interface ModelGeneratorSymbolic
extends ModelGenerator
    Interface for classes that generate a probabilistic model: given a particular model state (represented as a State object), they provide information about the outgoing transitions from that state.
